General Information

PAW Complete Calm Chews are tasty kangaroo based chews that contain key ingredients such as Tryptophan, B group vitamins and a blend of mutivitamins and nuttrients to support the general health and nervous function in dogs.

Common Uses

High levels of tryptophan to support and balance the wellbeing of dogs. B group vitamins to hep maintain a normal nervous function. Vitamins and minerals (nutrients) to help maintain a healthy immune system.

Ingredients

Kangaroo meat & by-product meal, rye flour, flaxseed meal, soya flour, sucrose, emulsifiers and binders, polyunsaturated fatty acids (with DHA/EPA), natural preservatives, L tryptophan, salt, vitamins (vitamin C, vitamin E, niacin (B3), riboflavin (B2), vitamin A, thiamine (B1), pyridoxine (B6), folic acid (B9), biotin (B7)), Natural flavour and colour, MSM, zinc sulfate, iron sulfate, manganese oxide, calcium iodate.
